ssess your transversal competences.\n2\ufe0f\u20e3 Improve your communication and public speaking skills.\n3\ufe0f\u20e3 Defend a commercial speech.\n4\ufe0f\u20e3 Speed up decision making.\n5\ufe0f\u20e3 Promote teamwork.\n\nIdeal for professionals looking to improve their interpersonal skills in an immersive, interactive and effective way!"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "SoftSkills_Logo_8100x1296px.png", "id": "1158856758691457", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974786_1158856762024790_8351105602424236604_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=w776LdQ6rLQQ7kNvgEvAUUY&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBA2_zOe08bm-OskCKcIVRUZgLsVpnT-JyRKOxPHYa0pg&oe=6752E2E9"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-portrait_1008x1440px.png", "id": "1001238441075007", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031591_1001238447741673_2783185145492224256_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=mtXg5QBXM5kQ7kNvgE4COcb&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAE4rIZig5z9qn-wELg9fNGjps74wT-OE2OhBJGc-502Q&oe=6752FBAF"}, {"file_name": "INVELON_Icon-512x512px.png", "id": "837105901661785", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75476759_837105904995118_1711704673161247418_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=XTxnsbaTdHoQ7kNvgFkcUvI&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDRbM0ZkC3byuB0WB69V9lA9hkCH4dJcB50hEbOAsaWxA&oe=6752F0F3"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Hero-cover_3000x900px.png", "id": "436545955954692", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974777_436545959288025_6494250809818469750_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=_2Spv3mY1ZIQ7kNvgF-_7hR&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBHfreO2qP-UC_mJKiPsHpMhLVctTOZT4cDxNs8lb9_Xw&oe=6752D8C5"}, {"file_name